Install instructions for libraries and applications in the PK source
code repository.


REQUIREMENTS
===============================================================================

 - PyQt4
 - supercollider


INSTALL
===============================================================================

Perform the following instructions to install everything in the
repository. This is what most people want to do.

$ python setup.py build
$ python setup.py install

The above script is separated into indepenent and re-usable peices,
which can be built and installed in the same manner.

setup_rtmidi.py     - python midi I/O
setup_scosc.py      - supercollider OSC
setup_pk.py         - PK modules/apps


UPDATES
===============================================================================

To download the newest code, type the following command in the repos
directory:

$ svn up
